      "comment": "NICKY ACES (4) bolted home by 5.5 lengths (17.35) at this track last time from box 1. Not generally a safe beginner but with a clean break can overcome the squeeze draw. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Ideally placed to take this out. TODOROKI (2) is a fast beginner who has shown good improvement at her last two starts, breaking through last time at this track over 300m. Expected to measure up again. ORSON DEL (6) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (24.08) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Must be included in calculations. RITA DUTTON (1) was unplaced here last start but gets her chance to atone.",
